WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:21.000
CHAPTERS THIRTEEN AND FOURTEEN OF THE GOSPEL OF MARK This is a LibriVox recording. All LibriVox recordings are in the public domain. For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibriVox.org.

00:21.000 --> 00:26.000
